gomodel:SYNGO_951  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Using a biochemical fractionation to prepare detergent-resistant postsynaptic density fractions, Fig. 6 shows that the 30 kDa band of Veli1 is present in this fraction. Velis 2, 3 both run at 25 kDa and this band is detected in the PSD fraction, but these two proteins cannot be distinguished from each other by immunoblotting.. Experimental description: \"Subcellular fractions of rat cerebral cortex were prepared by differential centrifugation as described previously\"" ;
